WEBVTT

00:00:08.230 --> 00:00:10.260
I feel great!

00:00:10.260 --> 00:00:14.180
They call me the bird that flies on
the turf. Of course I feel great!

00:00:19.330 --> 00:00:22.490
Seiun Sky-san, tell us what you're thinking.

00:00:22.490 --> 00:00:25.300
I won the Satsukishou, but I guess
I'm only the third favorite.

00:00:25.300 --> 00:00:27.850
Does that mean everyone will
be surprised if I win?

00:00:27.850 --> 00:00:28.940
Or maybe not?

00:00:33.820 --> 00:00:35.090
There's so many people.

00:00:35.090 --> 00:00:36.990
Please look this way.

00:00:36.990 --> 00:00:38.100
S-Sure.

00:00:38.100 --> 00:00:42.730
Special Week-san, do you
think you can win the Derby?

00:00:42.730 --> 00:00:45.150
Well… Uh…

00:00:46.290 --> 00:00:47.350
{\an8}Be silly!!

00:00:48.110 --> 00:00:49.590
I have to be silly?!

00:00:51.000 --> 00:00:57.074
Watch Online Movies and Series for FREE
www.osdb.link/lm

00:00:58.570 --> 00:01:00.990
{\an8}Japanese Derby

00:01:00.990 --> 00:01:05.000
{\an9}Japanese Derby

00:01:00.990 --> 00:01:05.000
{\an9}It'll take more than skill to win.

00:01:10.720 --> 00:01:15.940
Do you hear the fanfare as
we race towards the finish?

00:01:15.940 --> 00:01:22.470
I want to see that shining future with you

00:01:24.520 --> 00:01:30.820
{\an8}Umamusume

00:01:26.390 --> 00:01:30.690
{\an8}Pretty Derby

00:01:32.700 --> 00:01:38.420
If we just start to run, that's
where our story will begin

00:01:38.420 --> 00:01:43.440
It's always waiting right in front of us

00:01:43.440 --> 00:01:49.050
If you reach out just a little
more, we can seize that glory

00:01:49.050 --> 00:01:55.910
Aim for the top, challenge
them all, and it's off to the races

00:01:56.720 --> 00:02:01.910
Even the goddess of victory will be dazzled

00:02:01.910 --> 00:02:09.190
By your big debut that's just around the bend

00:02:09.190 --> 00:02:14.610
So can you hear the fanfare
as we race towards the finish?

00:02:14.610 --> 00:02:20.080
I want to see that shining future with you

00:02:20.080 --> 00:02:25.590
Let's overtake them all! It's
a track laid out just for you!

00:02:25.590 --> 00:02:33.350
Your dreams are at the finish if you believe

00:02:35.000 --> 00:02:39.010
{\an8}Race 5

00:02:35.000 --> 00:02:39.010
{\an8}The Derby With Rivals

00:02:42.470 --> 00:02:44.660
Spe, this is the last one!

00:02:44.660 --> 00:02:46.170
Get ready!

00:02:46.170 --> 00:02:46.890
Start!

00:02:53.180 --> 00:02:54.580
I'm so tired.

00:02:54.580 --> 00:02:56.370
You can do more.

00:02:56.370 --> 00:02:59.160
Why are you working us
so hard today, Trainer?

00:02:59.160 --> 00:03:01.570
You saw the way Taiki Shuttle ran, right?

00:03:02.020 --> 00:03:04.010
We need to train you to take shallow steps

00:03:04.010 --> 00:03:06.710
so that you won't slow down on hills.

00:03:07.330 --> 00:03:10.170
Spe-senpai's amazing…
How many sets has she run?

00:03:10.170 --> 00:03:12.810
The Derby's going to be
the longest race you've ever run.

00:03:12.810 --> 00:03:14.790
Just when you think you can't run anymore,
you've gotta face the hill.

00:03:15.250 --> 00:03:17.810
You need to be able to handle this, Spe!

00:03:21.620 --> 00:03:22.970
What's my time?

00:03:23.810 --> 00:03:25.510
42.8 seconds.

00:03:25.510 --> 00:03:26.980
Good job!

00:03:26.980 --> 00:03:29.310
That's my best time so far, right?

00:03:29.310 --> 00:03:32.820
Come on, you've got to
beat 40 seconds at least.

00:03:32.820 --> 00:03:34.940
I'm already at my limit!

00:03:34.940 --> 00:03:36.650
Well, that's too bad.

00:03:36.650 --> 00:03:41.430
If you can't push your limits, you're not
going to be able to beat those two.

00:03:41.430 --> 00:03:42.770
Trainer-san…

00:03:43.550 --> 00:03:44.030
Hmm?

00:03:44.030 --> 00:03:46.240
Time me again!

00:03:49.130 --> 00:03:54.830
One, two…

00:03:53.300 --> 00:03:54.830
Excuse me!

00:03:55.370 --> 00:03:56.180
She's fast!

00:03:56.180 --> 00:03:57.290
Who was that?

00:03:57.630 --> 00:03:59.930
I think it was Seiun Sky-san,

00:03:59.930 --> 00:04:02.170
but doesn't she normally
not take stuff seriously?

00:04:02.610 --> 00:04:04.520
<i>I can't afford to take it easy.</i>

00:04:04.520 --> 00:04:06.130
<i>The Derby's going to be tough.</i>

00:04:12.140 --> 00:04:13.400
What's wrong?

00:04:13.400 --> 00:04:15.400
It's rare to see you two exhausted.

00:04:15.790 --> 00:04:18.470
El Condor Pasa's so fast.

00:04:19.650 --> 00:04:21.900
Let's go one more time.

00:04:24.280 --> 00:04:25.770
Me, too.

00:04:27.780 --> 00:04:31.080
El Condor Pasa's doing pretty well.

00:04:31.080 --> 00:04:32.450
Rudolf…

00:04:32.450 --> 00:04:34.220
She's got speed and stamina.

00:04:34.220 --> 00:04:37.410
I'm sure the 2,400 meters won't
feel long to her at all.

00:04:37.410 --> 00:04:38.910
She's done five races and taken them all.

00:04:38.910 --> 00:04:40.420
If she takes the Derby without losing,

00:04:40.830 --> 00:04:44.930
she might just carve out a legend like yours.

00:04:44.930 --> 00:04:49.330
I was filled with so many
emotions when I took the Derby.

00:04:49.810 --> 00:04:51.950
I want her to experience the same thing.

00:04:53.050 --> 00:04:55.710
El Condor Pasa, I'll race you, too.

00:04:55.710 --> 00:04:57.390
I was waiting for this!

00:04:59.980 --> 00:05:03.610
It's amazing the three of
them made it on the cover.

00:05:03.610 --> 00:05:06.870
I can't wait to see who'll win.

00:05:07.790 --> 00:05:09.330
For the Derby…

00:05:09.860 --> 00:05:11.660
It's Maruzensky-san!

00:05:10.120 --> 00:05:13.060
{\an9}Maruzensky

00:05:11.660 --> 00:05:14.630
You need speed and stamina, of course,

00:05:14.630 --> 00:05:18.580
but they say the luckiest
horse girl always wins.

00:05:21.050 --> 00:05:23.390
What's wrong? Your face is all red.

00:05:23.390 --> 00:05:25.730
I was just thinking about
how beautiful she is…

00:05:25.730 --> 00:05:28.420
The girl with luck on her side will win, huh?

00:05:28.420 --> 00:05:29.420
That's right.

00:05:29.420 --> 00:05:31.140
That would be me, then!

00:05:31.140 --> 00:05:34.730
I got an extra can of juice from the
vending machine lottery a second ago.

00:05:32.720 --> 00:05:34.730
{\an8}Carrot Juice

00:05:34.730 --> 00:05:36.560
That's impressive.

00:05:36.560 --> 00:05:37.990
How nice…

00:05:37.990 --> 00:05:40.470
I never get lucky.

00:05:40.470 --> 00:05:41.950
Oh, I won another one free!

00:05:41.950 --> 00:05:43.380
Pretty lucky!

00:05:43.380 --> 00:05:44.780
How nice…

00:05:46.070 --> 00:05:47.780
I-I'm sorry!

00:05:47.780 --> 00:05:49.830
I'm really sorry…

00:05:50.630 --> 00:05:51.940
<i>I'm the only one who's not lucky.</i>

00:05:51.940 --> 00:05:53.540
It's okay.

00:05:53.860 --> 00:05:56.710
You're lucky that the cup didn't break.

00:05:57.690 --> 00:06:00.940
Anyway, I'll be watching all of you.

00:06:03.970 --> 00:06:06.770
<i>She's so pretty and cool!</i>

00:06:07.340 --> 00:06:08.850
Hey, Scarlet!

00:06:07.340 --> 00:06:09.970
{\an8}Class A

00:06:08.850 --> 00:06:09.970
You're on class duty today!

00:06:09.970 --> 00:06:12.400
I wanna start training right away!

00:06:12.400 --> 00:06:14.640
Don't slack off!

00:06:12.400 --> 00:06:14.340
{\an4}Tracen Academy
Team List

00:06:14.640 --> 00:06:16.540
Hey, McQueen.

00:06:15.970 --> 00:06:18.850
{\an9}Mejiro McQueen

00:06:18.290 --> 00:06:19.850
What do you want?

00:06:19.850 --> 00:06:23.360
{\an7}Team List
---
Team Rigil
Symboli Rudolf - Hishi Amazon
Taiki Shuttle - El Condor Pasa
Air Groove - Maruzensky - T.M Opera O
Narita Brian - Fuji Kiseki - Grass Wonder
---
Team Aschera
Golden Hint - Groom Monday
UN Cyclone - NPlace Me
Yasuda Repeat - Hidaka Warrior

00:06:20.200 --> 00:06:23.360
I'm busy choosing a team.

00:06:23.360 --> 00:06:25.110
Perfect timing.

00:06:25.110 --> 00:06:27.530
Could you join Spica?

00:06:28.980 --> 00:06:32.510
Do you understand what you're saying?

00:06:32.510 --> 00:06:36.050
I don't want to have a
rival in the same team,

00:06:36.050 --> 00:06:38.560
but Gold Ship is saying that
if I don't get you to join us,

00:06:38.560 --> 00:06:40.720
she's going to give me a piledriver.

00:06:40.720 --> 00:06:42.710
G-Gold Ship?

00:06:42.710 --> 00:06:43.920
You know her?

00:06:44.300 --> 00:06:49.170
Well, more like she doesn't stop bugging me,
even though I don't show interest.

00:07:04.860 --> 00:07:06.980
Hot mustard!

00:07:14.190 --> 00:07:15.620
The eraser!

00:07:14.910 --> 00:07:15.620
Oh my…

00:07:27.710 --> 00:07:28.820
Oh my…

00:07:29.730 --> 00:07:32.590
She seems to like me for some reason.

00:07:32.590 --> 00:07:35.850
Maybe it's like me and the Prez?

00:07:41.560 --> 00:07:44.300
Suzuka-san, let me go again.

00:07:44.300 --> 00:07:45.420
Spe-chan…

00:07:45.940 --> 00:07:47.690
Don't push yourself.

00:07:48.150 --> 00:07:49.500
Suzuka-san…

00:07:51.010 --> 00:07:52.200
Right!

00:07:53.150 --> 00:07:55.310
I was ninth place in the Derby.

00:07:55.310 --> 00:07:57.500
It was pretty long for me,

00:07:57.500 --> 00:07:59.920
and I couldn't push myself hard enough.

00:07:59.920 --> 00:08:01.710
I see.

00:08:02.430 --> 00:08:05.700
How do you overcome your limits?

00:08:05.700 --> 00:08:07.240
Well…

00:08:07.240 --> 00:08:10.060
You love carrots, so how about
putting some at the finish line?

00:08:10.060 --> 00:08:11.180
Hey, Suzuka-san!

00:08:11.180 --> 00:08:13.270
Give me a serious answer.

00:08:17.180 --> 00:08:19.570
To be the number one horse girl in Japan…

00:08:19.570 --> 00:08:21.660
The dream and promise I made with my mother.

00:08:21.660 --> 00:08:23.370
I want it to come true through the Derby.

00:08:23.370 --> 00:08:27.650
I also have a dream I want to come true,
now that I've joined Spica.

00:08:27.650 --> 00:08:28.270
Huh?

00:08:28.820 --> 00:08:33.050
Coming up, I have the
Takarazuka Kinen, Mainichi Okan,

00:08:33.050 --> 00:08:36.910
the Tennoushou in the Fall,
the Japan Cup, and then after that…

00:08:39.290 --> 00:08:40.430
Well, it's still a secret.

00:08:40.430 --> 00:08:43.210
No fair! Tell me!

00:08:43.210 --> 00:08:45.590
If you win the Derby, I'll tell you.

00:08:45.590 --> 00:08:48.630
You're such a tease, Suzuka-san!

00:08:50.210 --> 00:08:51.940
This is my plan.

00:08:51.940 --> 00:08:53.080
Understand?

00:08:53.080 --> 00:08:54.300
No problem.

00:08:54.300 --> 00:08:57.640
Make sure you watch closely for any
moves that Special Week might make.

00:08:54.300 --> 00:08:57.640
{\an4}Japanese Derby Course Map

00:08:58.000 --> 00:09:02.270
I am concerned about Spe-chan, but
I'll trust in my own judgment as I run.

00:09:02.270 --> 00:09:03.530
Of course.

00:09:03.530 --> 00:09:05.550
You've got good racing instincts.

00:09:05.550 --> 00:09:08.230
As long as you put in
the effort, you can't lose.

00:09:08.230 --> 00:09:08.860
Right!

00:09:14.190 --> 00:09:16.700
Teio, where's your trainer?

00:09:17.090 --> 00:09:19.690
I came to help you…

00:09:19.690 --> 00:09:22.330
That's a daughter of the
Mejiro family for you!

00:09:22.330 --> 00:09:24.020
You have perfectly balanced—

00:09:24.710 --> 00:09:26.780
Hey! What are you doing?

00:09:26.780 --> 00:09:29.420
I guess McQueen won't fit in here.

00:09:29.420 --> 00:09:31.570
That's what I've been saying since yesterday!

00:09:31.570 --> 00:09:33.300
Good work, Teio!

00:09:35.790 --> 00:09:39.220
Mejiro McQueen, please sign here!

00:09:39.220 --> 00:09:40.950
I'll be sitting in first.

00:09:43.580 --> 00:09:47.270
But I want to run with you.

00:09:49.940 --> 00:09:52.730
Hey, you don't have to cry!

00:09:52.730 --> 00:09:56.210
I'm not saying I won't join.

00:09:56.210 --> 00:09:57.890
McQueen is surprisingly…

00:09:57.890 --> 00:10:00.240
…pretty easy to handle.

00:10:04.830 --> 00:10:07.540
You're going to run with me?!

00:10:07.540 --> 00:10:09.860
Try passing me.

00:10:10.450 --> 00:10:12.090
Thank you.

00:10:12.090 --> 00:10:14.550
Spe, overcome your limits!

00:10:14.550 --> 00:10:18.270
If you can't beat 40 seconds,
you'll never be able to win the Derby!

00:10:18.270 --> 00:10:18.930
Right!

00:10:18.930 --> 00:10:20.030
Let's go!

00:10:20.030 --> 00:10:21.430
Ready…

00:10:21.430 --> 00:10:22.430
Start!

00:10:26.300 --> 00:10:28.210
<i>Sh-She's fast.</i>

00:10:28.210 --> 00:10:31.270
<i>I want to catch up to Suzuka-san.</i>

00:10:31.270 --> 00:10:33.070
<i>Someday when I race her, I…</i>

00:10:33.750 --> 00:10:35.570
<i>That's why I need to do this!</i>

00:10:35.980 --> 00:10:40.810
Derby!

00:10:58.220 --> 00:11:00.800
<i>Spe-chan's getting faster.</i>

00:11:01.820 --> 00:11:03.750
Trainer-san, what's my time?

00:11:04.370 --> 00:11:07.690
Oh man, I forgot to start the time.

00:11:07.690 --> 00:11:11.500
Hey, do your job!

00:11:09.530 --> 00:11:11.500
{\an8}My bad.

00:11:15.550 --> 00:11:18.220
What are you guys doing?

00:11:18.990 --> 00:11:22.990
{\an8}Umamusume

00:11:18.990 --> 00:11:22.990
{\an8}Pretty Derby

00:11:27.260 --> 00:11:29.620
It's finally time for the Japanese Derby.

00:11:30.430 --> 00:11:31.660
Watch over her.

00:11:32.620 --> 00:11:35.130
{\an8}Japanese Derby

00:11:38.710 --> 00:11:43.970
{\an8}Japanese Derby

00:11:39.710 --> 00:11:41.730
<i>It's finally that time of year!</i>

00:11:41.730 --> 00:11:46.220
<i>It's the festival of horse girls! The Tokyo
Yushun, a.k.a the Japanese Derby!</i>

00:11:43.970 --> 00:11:46.220
{\an8}Horse Girl
Castellas

00:11:43.970 --> 00:11:46.220
{\an9}Corn

00:11:43.970 --> 00:11:46.220
{\an6}Japanese
Derby

00:11:46.220 --> 00:11:48.970
The more than 150,000 spectators
are filling the seats!

00:11:49.300 --> 00:11:51.150
Take-san, what do you think?

00:11:51.150 --> 00:11:53.880
We've got plenty of stars this year.

00:11:53.880 --> 00:11:58.070
There are eighteen qualifying
horse girls with us today, and
plenty of rivalries among them.

00:11:58.070 --> 00:12:02.150
Which horse girl will win
glory out there on the track?

00:12:02.810 --> 00:12:04.160
Oh, she's here.

00:12:06.130 --> 00:12:08.410
H-Hi there.

00:12:08.750 --> 00:12:10.850
Looks like you're nervous.

00:12:10.850 --> 00:12:14.390
I'm worried if I'll be
able to surpass my limits.

00:12:15.310 --> 00:12:16.210
What are you…

00:12:16.710 --> 00:12:19.110
You practiced hill running so many times.

00:12:19.110 --> 00:12:21.670
Now, you've just gotta have
as much fun as you can.

00:12:21.670 --> 00:12:23.370
R-Right.

00:12:23.370 --> 00:12:24.380
Here you go.

00:12:25.140 --> 00:12:29.220
{\an8}Good luck!

00:12:26.100 --> 00:12:29.220
Is this a four leaf clover?

00:12:29.220 --> 00:12:29.970
Yeah!

00:12:29.970 --> 00:12:31.690
We all looked for it together.

00:12:31.690 --> 00:12:34.990
The luckiest horse wins the Derby.

00:12:34.990 --> 00:12:36.240
You guys…

00:12:36.240 --> 00:12:38.620
We couldn't really find one…

00:12:38.620 --> 00:12:40.660
But McQueen found that one for you.

00:12:40.660 --> 00:12:43.750
I just happened to spot one.

00:12:43.750 --> 00:12:46.550
She's helping out our team already.

00:12:46.550 --> 00:12:49.050
You have to reward someone
when they're working so hard.

00:12:49.050 --> 00:12:51.750
Now luck will be on your side, Spe-chan.

00:12:51.750 --> 00:12:52.970
You guys…

00:12:52.970 --> 00:12:54.900
Mejiro McQueen-san, you too.

00:12:54.900 --> 00:12:56.420
Thank you all!

00:12:56.420 --> 00:12:58.940
I'm really happy!

00:13:00.270 --> 00:13:02.630
I'll be going!

00:13:04.260 --> 00:13:07.240
<i>Now, it's time for the horse girls to enter!</i>

00:13:07.240 --> 00:13:11.010
<i>El Condor Pasa, #1, will be entering later.</i>

00:13:11.010 --> 00:13:16.220
<i>First, #3 in the Yayoishou,
and #2 in the Satsukishou…</i>

00:13:16.220 --> 00:13:17.660
<i>It's King Halo!</i>

00:13:16.410 --> 00:13:18.360
King Halo

00:13:20.570 --> 00:13:23.350
<i>Will she overcome her
disgrace in the Satsukishou?</i>

00:13:23.350 --> 00:13:26.290
<i>Show us a miracle, Special Week!</i>

00:13:30.900 --> 00:13:32.680
<i>It's even more amazing than the other races.</i>

00:13:32.680 --> 00:13:34.660
<i>So this is the Derby…</i>

00:13:35.060 --> 00:13:38.830
She succeeded with her diet.
I think she can do this.

00:13:38.830 --> 00:13:42.490
<i>She's the winner of the Satsukishou,
and she wants her second crown!</i>

00:13:42.490 --> 00:13:45.270
<i>It's the trickster, Seiun Sky!</i>

00:13:45.270 --> 00:13:47.290
<i>She's got more presence now.</i>

00:13:54.380 --> 00:13:55.610
El Condor Pasa…

00:13:55.610 --> 00:13:56.640
Y-Yes?!

00:13:56.990 --> 00:14:00.020
Hmm? So you get nervous too, huh?

00:14:00.020 --> 00:14:02.850
Well, it's my first time.

00:14:02.850 --> 00:14:05.370
There are no absolutes in a race, they say.

00:14:05.370 --> 00:14:07.210
I don't blame you for getting nervous.

00:14:08.100 --> 00:14:12.240
But a horse girl born to dominate
doesn't need to hear kind words.

00:14:12.240 --> 00:14:15.660
El Condor Pasa, show your
absolute best performance.

00:14:16.260 --> 00:14:17.120
Understood?

00:14:19.130 --> 00:14:21.600
Yes, I'll win.

00:14:21.600 --> 00:14:23.130
I absolutely will.

00:14:25.050 --> 00:14:28.590
<i>We have our last horse, Bracket 1, Number 1.</i>

00:14:28.590 --> 00:14:30.390
<i>She's won five out of five races.</i>

00:14:30.390 --> 00:14:32.510
<i>She's the invincible bird that knows no loss,</i>

00:14:32.510 --> 00:14:34.510
<i>El Condor Pasa!</i>

00:14:36.070 --> 00:14:38.220
<i>She's the clear favorite.</i>

00:14:38.670 --> 00:14:40.770
<i>I will dominate.</i>

00:14:40.770 --> 00:14:43.730
Everyone's ready for a fight today.

00:14:55.120 --> 00:14:57.220
Spe looks so small.

00:14:57.820 --> 00:14:59.500
Trainer…

00:14:59.500 --> 00:15:01.010
You've got those backwards.

00:15:01.010 --> 00:15:02.580
You're getting too nervous.

00:15:02.580 --> 00:15:05.380
I'm not nervous at all!

00:15:05.760 --> 00:15:08.630
<i>You can do this, Spe.</i>

00:15:08.630 --> 00:15:10.980
<i>We're all ready now.</i>

00:15:08.630 --> 00:15:13.390
{\an8}Tokyo

00:15:10.980 --> 00:15:13.390
<i>It's time for the Japanese Derby fanfare.</i>

00:15:33.500 --> 00:15:37.240
<i>It's almost time for the climax of the event!</i>

00:15:41.870 --> 00:15:44.670
<i>The festival of horse girls,
the Japanese Derby.</i>

00:15:45.220 --> 00:15:45.880
<i>It's time to…</i>

00:15:48.110 --> 00:15:49.540
<i>…start!</i>

00:15:49.540 --> 00:15:52.300
<i>Who will take the lead of the pack?</i>

00:15:52.300 --> 00:15:54.030
<i>We have Seiun Sky in the lead.</i>

00:15:54.030 --> 00:15:55.850
<i>No, King Halo from the inside.</i>

00:15:55.850 --> 00:15:57.530
<i>Yasuda Repeat has come up front!</i>

00:15:57.530 --> 00:15:59.520
<i>They're all fighting hard for that lead!</i>

00:15:59.520 --> 00:16:00.910
You can do it!

00:16:00.910 --> 00:16:02.130
Go, go!

00:16:02.130 --> 00:16:02.940
Spe-chan…

00:16:02.940 --> 00:16:05.060
Go!

00:16:03.420 --> 00:16:05.060
Go for it, Spe-chan!

00:16:11.280 --> 00:16:13.700
<i>The leaders are exiting the first
turn and heading for the second.</i>

00:16:13.700 --> 00:16:16.950
<i>Which horse girl will take the lead?</i>

00:16:18.950 --> 00:16:20.910
Go, Spe!

00:16:22.620 --> 00:16:24.460
<i>They're making the second turn
and crossing the track.</i>

00:16:24.460 --> 00:16:26.460
<i>Seiun Sky is in second.</i>

00:16:26.460 --> 00:16:29.210
<i>King Halo is in first!</i>

00:16:29.210 --> 00:16:31.590
<i>She's changed her strategy
from her last race!</i>

00:16:31.590 --> 00:16:34.100
<i>I won't let you take over.</i>

00:16:34.700 --> 00:16:36.390
<i>That's fine by me.</i>

00:16:36.390 --> 00:16:41.390
<i>Special Week is staying in the middle!</i>

00:16:42.090 --> 00:16:43.730
<i>The slipstream!</i>

00:16:44.140 --> 00:16:46.940
Looks like that training is paying off.

00:16:48.500 --> 00:16:50.450
<i>Seiun Sky-san is over there…</i>

00:16:52.340 --> 00:16:55.540
<i>I wonder where El-chan is…</i>

00:16:57.060 --> 00:16:58.700
<i>I'm right here.</i>

00:16:59.500 --> 00:17:02.680
<i>El Condor Pasa is heading up the rear.</i>

00:17:04.790 --> 00:17:08.170
King Halo is losing her cool.

00:17:08.170 --> 00:17:10.460
I don't blame her for getting anxious.

00:17:10.460 --> 00:17:12.340
<i>They're making the third turn.</i>

00:17:12.340 --> 00:17:14.170
<i>King Halo is in the lead.</i>

00:17:14.170 --> 00:17:16.490
<i>When will Seiun Sky make her move?</i>

00:17:16.490 --> 00:17:19.750
<i>And Special Week and El Condor
Pasa, for that matter!</i>

00:17:20.720 --> 00:17:23.490
<i>I have… I have to take a further lead.</i>

00:17:23.490 --> 00:17:24.680
<i>I'm not letting that happen.</i>

00:17:25.250 --> 00:17:27.310
<i>Will someone make their move soon?</i>

00:17:32.400 --> 00:17:34.610
<i>I'm sure they're going to
come from behind real fast.</i>

00:17:34.610 --> 00:17:36.450
<i>I need to hurry up and make my move.</i>

00:17:37.110 --> 00:17:38.650
Wh-What?

00:17:40.080 --> 00:17:43.750
Seiun Sky is making her
move on the fourth corner!

00:17:43.750 --> 00:17:46.290
<i>She's caught up with King Halo!</i>

00:17:48.700 --> 00:17:51.850
<i>Seiun Sky took the lead!</i>

00:17:51.850 --> 00:17:54.180
<i>Is that it for King Halo?</i>

00:17:55.290 --> 00:17:57.680
<i>Seiun Sky is in the lead!</i>

00:18:04.850 --> 00:18:06.680
<i>Special Week!</i>

00:18:06.680 --> 00:18:09.090
<i>Here comes Special Week!</i>

00:18:09.990 --> 00:18:11.190
Go!

00:18:11.190 --> 00:18:13.620
<i>So you've come, Spe-chan!</i>

00:18:13.620 --> 00:18:14.690
<i>But…!</i>

00:18:15.090 --> 00:18:17.070
<i>There's less than 400 meters left!</i>

00:18:19.130 --> 00:18:21.340
<i>Spe-chan can't handle hills.</i>

00:18:26.470 --> 00:18:27.500
It's the hill!

00:18:27.500 --> 00:18:28.920
She's using her shallow stride!

00:18:31.580 --> 00:18:33.340
<i>I've got stamina left.</i>

00:18:33.840 --> 00:18:35.180
<i>Hills…</i>

00:18:36.270 --> 00:18:38.680
…are all about guts!

00:18:38.680 --> 00:18:42.020
<i>Oh my! Special Week has
caught up to Seiun Sky!</i>

00:18:43.380 --> 00:18:45.600
<i>She's passing her! She's passing her!</i>

00:18:46.430 --> 00:18:49.030
<i>Why? I'm running as fast as I can!</i>

00:18:50.690 --> 00:18:52.090
No…

00:18:52.090 --> 00:18:53.690
No!

00:18:54.050 --> 00:18:55.740
<i>She ran right past her!</i>

00:18:55.740 --> 00:18:57.430
<i>Special Week's up front!</i>

00:18:58.690 --> 00:19:00.320
Damn it!

00:19:02.530 --> 00:19:05.290
<i>Oh, wow! That's some fast
movement from the inside!</i>

00:19:05.290 --> 00:19:07.890
She's come! She's come!

00:19:07.890 --> 00:19:09.430
<i>She's flying like a bird out there…</i>

00:19:09.430 --> 00:19:10.330
<i>It's…</i>

00:19:10.750 --> 00:19:13.540
<i>…El Condor Pasa!</i>

00:19:16.110 --> 00:19:17.180
<i>She's catching up!</i>

00:19:17.180 --> 00:19:18.970
<i>She's catching up to Special Week!</i>

00:19:19.340 --> 00:19:20.800
All right! Catch up to her!

00:19:20.800 --> 00:19:22.110
She's come, huh?

00:19:22.110 --> 00:19:24.260
She's super fast!

00:19:24.260 --> 00:19:26.370
<i>El Condor Pasa's catching
up with frightening speed!</i>

00:19:26.370 --> 00:19:27.760
<i>There's 200 meters left!</i>

00:19:27.760 --> 00:19:30.520
<i>The favorite has made her appearance at last!</i>

00:19:30.520 --> 00:19:31.900
She's taken the lead in an instant!

00:19:31.900 --> 00:19:33.270
She's fast…

00:19:33.270 --> 00:19:35.700
<i>El Condor Pasa is way too fast!</i>

00:19:51.180 --> 00:19:53.000
<i>Don't give up yet.</i>

00:19:53.490 --> 00:19:54.390
<i>This is where…</i>

00:19:55.000 --> 00:19:57.250
<i>This is where you…</i>

00:19:57.250 --> 00:19:59.150
<i>…overcome your limits!</i>

00:20:00.260 --> 00:20:01.550
<i>They're in the last 50 meters!</i>

00:20:01.550 --> 00:20:03.380
<i>The finish line is right in front of them!</i>

00:20:03.380 --> 00:20:04.590
<i>All right!</i>

00:20:05.540 --> 00:20:08.590
<i>I'm sure my mom is cheering
me on right now.</i>

00:20:08.590 --> 00:20:10.260
<i>I don't want to give up yet!</i>

00:20:14.600 --> 00:20:16.560
Spe-chan!

00:20:16.560 --> 00:20:18.020
<i>Suzuka-san…</i>

00:20:18.610 --> 00:20:19.780
<i>Everyone…</i>

00:20:24.820 --> 00:20:27.200
<i>Special Week is regaining her wind!</i>

00:20:29.550 --> 00:20:30.520
No way!

00:20:38.210 --> 00:20:42.630
Just who will win the Derby?!

00:21:00.890 --> 00:21:04.360
<i>Will it be El Condor Pasa or Special Week?</i>

00:21:10.850 --> 00:21:11.620
{\an8}Photo

00:21:10.850 --> 00:21:11.620
{\an8}Tokyo

00:21:11.620 --> 00:21:12.620
A photo…

00:21:12.620 --> 00:21:13.660
…finish?

00:21:15.990 --> 00:21:18.500
The Japanese Derby this year will
come down to a photo finish.

00:21:18.870 --> 00:21:20.920
<i>It's a photo finish!</i>

00:21:19.490 --> 00:21:20.920
S-Spe-chan!

00:21:21.830 --> 00:21:23.790
S-Suzuka-san…

00:21:23.790 --> 00:21:24.420
Spe-chan!

00:21:25.190 --> 00:21:28.260
I overcame my limits…

00:21:28.730 --> 00:21:29.590
Yeah.

00:21:31.430 --> 00:21:35.510
I guess my friends in Spica turned out
to be my carrots at the finish line.

00:21:44.900 --> 00:21:46.900
{\an5}Dead Heat

00:21:44.900 --> 00:21:46.900
{\an7}Tokyo

00:21:46.900 --> 00:21:48.730
A dead heat?

00:21:48.730 --> 00:21:50.120
A dead heat!

00:21:50.120 --> 00:21:51.370
A dead heat?!

00:21:51.370 --> 00:21:53.320
<i>I can't believe it!</i>

00:21:53.320 --> 00:21:55.370
<i>This Derby has two winners!</i>

00:21:55.370 --> 00:21:58.920
<i>El Condor Pasa and Special Week!</i>

00:21:58.920 --> 00:22:01.090
I-I did it!

00:22:01.090 --> 00:22:03.410
Suzuka-san, I did it!

00:22:10.530 --> 00:22:13.180
Special Week's pretty good.

00:22:14.300 --> 00:22:15.730
Yeah.

00:22:16.250 --> 00:22:18.520
I'll be winning outright next time.

00:22:19.260 --> 00:22:20.790
Bring it on.

00:22:22.250 --> 00:22:24.300
Spe-chan, thank you.

00:22:24.300 --> 00:22:25.150
Huh?

00:22:31.790 --> 00:22:35.620
That was the funnest race I've had so far!

00:22:38.730 --> 00:22:39.840
Me, too!

00:22:39.840 --> 00:22:41.130
El-chan, thank you!

00:22:46.060 --> 00:22:48.660
<i>Mom, did you see me out there?</i>

00:22:49.305 --> 00:23:49.309
